{"tid":1312822,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［重要呼籲］咁多位兄弟  係時候真正咁升級行動","createTime":"2019-07-13T15:13:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T16:48:46.000Z","uid":177213,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"de405027b09da9db216f5b7a4b23d7b67f22e3d8","tid":1312822,"uid":177213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T15:13:30.000Z","msg":"經歴過咁多場戰役<br />\n<br />\n死咗4個人<br />\n<br />\n記者又比狗打<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日連16歲00後𡃁仔都比狗迫到跳橋</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我想問<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">各位手足係咪仲要繼續比狗撚？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n驚比狗拉？乜你唔知<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人而家已經退無可退喇咩？</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n官逼民反<br />\n<br />\n比人鬧暴徒又如何,請記住人性就係<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勝者為王 敗者為寇！<br />\n<br />\n</span></span>Show到我哋有Power,迫到政府回應訴求,民意自然會返嚟<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n各位,係時候比班狗知邊個先係主人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請咁多位以後唔好再吝嗇自己嘅拳頭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係時候上喇！</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f10d4614554b48d284b9cca356a5d429046637a1","tid":1312822,"uid":177213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T15:13:34.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"abc7467ec75d2f2a35468d44eb4ca116043c5031","tid":1312822,"uid":177213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T15:14:01.000Z","msg":"推到上熱門！"},{"pid":"2b089a3ab7006572aa457f917711e932f908e31a","tid":1312822,"uid":177213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T15:14:17.000Z","msg":"係時候上喇！"},{"pid":"e1e5fc6e7ae0ef8e5523a740b8fdc8c00b680d01","tid":1312822,"uid":177213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T15: